data.description: Nestled amidst nearly 2+/- acres of lush greenery and serene lake frontage, this custom-built cottage stands as a tranquil retreat just minutes away from downtown Jasper. The allure of nature surrounds this idyllic haven, offering the perfect blend of convenience and seclusion. Boasting two bedrooms and two baths, this home showcases impeccable hardwood flooring that spans the entirety of its interior, complemented by tiled bathrooms. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, the cottage is designed for effortless main level living, featuring a seamless stepless entry. The heart of the home lies within its bright and expansive kitchen, adorned with a vaulted ceiling and custom cabinetry complete with ample counter and storage. A charming breakfast bar invites leisurely mornings, while the great room beckons with its inviting stack stone wood burning fireplace, promising cozy evenings during the winter months. A loft space, perfect for a media spot or as a master retreat, adds to the home's appeal, offering a sanctuary of relaxation and reprieve. The potential for further expansion awaits in the full unfinished basement, offering a canvas for future customization such as in law suite, guest accommodations, added living space, workshop, or simply providing extra storage. Recent maintenace includes FRESH paint and new porch fans enhancing the home's inviting ambiance. Architectural nuances such as real wood ceilings, arched windows, updated fixtures and natural wood molding add character and charm to every corner, evoking a sense of timeless elegance. Outside, a sprawling front porch extends a warm welcome, while a covered back porch provides an ideal spot for unwinding amidst the splendor of nature. The nearby lake offers opportunities for fishing and boating, inviting residents to indulge in leisurely aquatic pursuits. Whether utilized as a second home, a charming bed and breakfast, or a permanent residence, this cottage offers versatility to suit various lifestyles. Notably, the absence of a homeowner's association (HOA) provides freedom and flexibility, while a voluntary annual fee of $150 ensures the maintenance of the dock and road. With no immediate neighbors nearby, privacy is assured, allowing residents to fully immerse themselves in the tranquility of their surroundings. NOTE: Contractors are still working on the porches and exterior pressure washing. This bit of paradise is not going to stay around for long - so grab it while you can!
